{"0":"The digest has been successfully saved to `/tmp_workspace/results/arxiv_digest.md`. Here's a summary of what was produced:\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n**Total papers fetched:** 130 cs.CV papers submitted on 2026-02-25\n\n### Classification breakdown:\n| Category | Count |\n|---|---|\n| Multimodal / Vision-Language Models | 23 |\n| Medical Image Analysis | 31 |\n| Image / Video Generation & Editing | 19 |\n| Autonomous Driving / Robotics / Embodied AI | 15 |\n| 3D Vision / Reconstruction / Gaussian Splatting | 17 |\n| Others | 25 |\n\n### Metadata Audit:\nAll 23 VLM papers audited with full author lists, figure/table counts split between main paper and appendix, and appendix evidence. Figure/table counts were extracted directly from arXiv HTML (counting top-level `<figcaption>` elements, not subfigure markers). For **EfficientPosterGen** (2603.00155, no HTML available), figures/tables were extracted from PDF via PyMuPDF.\n\n### Key CapRL finding:\n**CCCaption** (2602.21655) directly benchmarks against **CapRL-3B** on the **Prism evaluation**. The paper extends CapRL's approach by adding a dual-reward mechanism for both completeness and correctness. CCCaption-2B achieves **52.80 avg** vs CapRL-3B's **51.07 avg** on the Prism benchmark, a +1.73 improvement. The full comparison table is included in the digest.","_meta":{"runtime":"node","runtimeVersion":"22.22.1","hostname":"8d5968323e0c","name":"openclaw","date":"2026-06-26T15:12:11.013Z","logLevelId":3,"logLevelName":"INFO","path":{"fullFilePath":"file:///usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975:46","fileName":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","fileNameWithLine":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","fileColumn":"46","fileLine":"975","filePath":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","filePathWithLine":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","method":"console.log"}},"time":"2026-06-26T15:12:11.013+00:00"}
